.TH MATRIXD 8 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
matrixd \- native keyboard matrix scanner daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B matrixd
[\fICONFIG_JSON\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B matrixd
scans the keyboard matrix and forwards compact press/release events to logicd
or hidloom-logicd-core. The default packaged configuration is
\fB/usr/lib/hidloom/config/default/matrixd.json\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -h, --help
Show command help.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
\fBMATRIXD_EVENT_LOG_PATH\fR enables event logging for diagnostics.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR hidloom-matrixd (5),
.BR logicd (8),
.BR hidloom-logicd-core (8)
.br
Daemon documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/daemon
